This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image manipulation and style transfer. Additionally, it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it involves the use of neural networks for image processing. The Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category is also a possibility as it deals with image stylisation. Finally, the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category may also be relevant as the paper discusses the production of large size, high-quality stylisation.
